Subject: Re: [T2] Wiring  'passages' from front to back on Westy?

Why not run them alongside the main wiring loom?  It runs along the right
hand side of the centre section (at least it does on a RHD - not sure if a
LHD is reversed).  There is enough space to get a few more wires through.

